    <h1>Singly Linked List Visualizer</h1>
    <p>Enter a value (e.g., a number or string) and use the buttons to interact with the list.</p>

    <div class="controls">
        <input type="text" id="value-input" placeholder="Enter value">
        <button id="insert-head">Insert at Head</button>
        <button id="insert-tail">Insert at Tail</button>
        <button id="delete-value">Delete by Value</button>
        <button id="search-value">Search</button>
    </div>

