            <li><strong>API services:</strong> Integrate with services like Abstract API or ZeroBounce, which can verify email deliverability, check for disposable emails, and validate against real-time data.</li>
            <li><strong>Combined approach:</strong> Use client-side regex for immediate feedback (as in this demo) but always follow up with server-side validation to confirm the email's validity and prevent security issues like injection attacks.</li>
